You're so shameless.

324
00:29:16,212 --> 00:29:17,714
What? I knew you'd discard it.

325
00:29:17,797 --> 00:29:19,883
North Winds, Green Dragons, White Dragons,

326
00:29:19,966 --> 00:29:21,342
Triplets Hand, and Half Flush,

327
00:29:21,426 --> 00:29:24,429
