yesterday's happiness back today?"

375
00:31:35,101 --> 00:31:38,771
When I heard that, I really couldn't help
but roll my eyes at her.

376
00:31:38,855 --> 00:31:41,566
Yes, you heard me right. I rolled my eyes.

377
00:31:41,649 --> 00:31:45,361
Your ability to see and roll your eyes
are two separate matters.

378
00:31:45,445 --> 00:31:47,030
